System Monitor

A simple Python-based system monitoring tool that displays real-time information about CPU usage, RAM usage, and running processes.

Features

- Real-time CPU usage monitoring
- RAM usage (total, used, percentage)
- Displays top 10 running processes
- Shows process names and PIDs
- Auto-refresh every few seconds
- Error handling for disappearing or inaccessible processes

Technologies Used

- Python
- psutil
- os
- time

How to Run

1. Install required library:
-> pip install psutil

2. Run the script:
-> python system_monitor.py

